
news_xml2alvis.pl  <XML suffix> <meta suffix> <orig suffix> <root dir> <out dir> <N per output dir> <Meta file encoding>

	Scans recursively <root dir>, looking for files of these suffixes:
           <XML suffix>   news XML file
           <meta suffix>  its Meta file
           <orig suffix>  the original HTML file
	and outputs Alvis XML under <out dir>, each record in a file of its
	own, <N per output dir> per subdirectory.  <Meta file encoding> 
	gives the encoding of the Meta files.
        
   
